<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/30629342">关羽和张飞在历史上确有其人吗？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4434133" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">为什么两个人名字这么巧合？除三国志和引用三国志的史书外还有哪里提到？</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
